title: Haikyuu!! - Primary Target (Doujinshi)
description:
Pair: Kageyama Tobio x Hinata Shouyou

When Kageyama's desires grows out of control, he finds himself drawing closer and closer to Hinata. Unable to stop himself anymore, he corners Hinata and tells him to "run away". A confused Hinata doesn't understand Kageyama's suffering and unexpectedly finds himself a target of Kageyama's frustrated emotions.

Part 1: Primary Target Zenpen
Part 2: Primary Target Kouhen
